                        in Osterreich,</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pe__michael_zinkk_QGW_II_II_1944">Michel Zingk, sein <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_zinkk_QGW_II_I_1645">bruder</roleName></rs></rs>,
